晚上：开始是配音练习，关掉声音仅看视频，然后把音频配置出来；把这个场景演绎出来



Morning: Use the APP - Classic Repeater to familiarize each sentence of the video.

Afternoon: Melody  teacher analyze every sentence  and help us master each sentence.

Evening: At the beginning, it is a dubbing practice. Turn off the sound and just watch the video, then configure the audio; Then interpret the scene.



感悟总结：

